    {
      "para_id": "Q001829.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters presented this ( seal ) to Babati , the archivist , the royal comptroller , the military governor of Maškan-šarrum , the governor of Awal , the administrator of ..., the canal inspector of the irrigated lands , ... Belat-suḫnir and Belat-terraban , the brother of Abi-simti , his beloved mother , his servant ."
    }
  ],
